data.description: Welcome to Sherman Hills the best kept secret in Hernando County! You have to see this home! This 4 bedroom home has the perfect layout, check out the floorplan in the pictures! Split floorplan with the primary bedroom on the opposite side of the home from the other 3 bedrooms!  Spare room for an office and a formal dining room on either side of you when you first enter the home.  Sprawling living room space combines the front foyer, breakfast nook and kitchen in this open concept home.  The kitchen features wood cabinets and a spacious pantry.  The oversized primary bedroom features a private door access to the back screened porch and an in-suite bathroom with a garden tub, walk-in shower, dual vanities and 2 large walk-in closets.  The 3 other bedrooms are a perfect size and share the second bathroom that has an updated vanity and granite top.  3 doors from 3 different rooms provide access to the beautiful back screened porch that overlooks the golf course and is a perfect place to entertain and relax.  Low HOA of $200 per year and you get $50 back if you pay in full by the due date!  Centrally located in the state at the intersection of I-75 and SR-50 you can quickly get to the airport, downtown Tampa, beaches, lakes, trails, Disney and some of the best springs in Florida including Weeki Wachee, Three Sisters, Rock, Rainbow, Silver Glen, Juniper, Alexander and tons more! Live your best Florida lifestyle and schedule your showing today! Check out the virtual 360 walkthrough and floorplan!  You just can't find a better layout and a more peaceful location at this price point!  Come see it for yourself!
